# thoth_pack_assignment_bulk

Applies one or more compliance packs to all agents or scoped subsets (agent_ids, fleet_ids, endpoint_ids).

## Example Usage

```hcl
resource "thoth_pack_assignment_bulk" "privacy_baseline" {
  pack_ids    = ["soc2-type2", "gdpr-ai-agents"]
  environment = "prod"
  fleet_ids   = ["fleet-finance", "fleet-legal"]
}
```

